data.description: This is YOUR opportunity to make this 3/2 split bedroom SMART HOME, 2021 D.R. Horton Aria floor plan your own. SOLAR PANELS, STAINLESS STEEL kitchen appliances, QUARTZ kitchen countertops, and WASHER/DRYER are included.    This gated Village of Entrada community has some of Southwest Florida's LOWEST HOA fees, and is in a NO FLOOD ZONE.  Appreciate a quiet CUL-DE-SAC of nice neighbors on a smaller street?  Well you got it! In the back of your home when you want to really unwind, you have the natural preserves just at your back door offering you peace and privacy.   BEACH-ENTRY RESORT STYLE POOL includes lap lanes, a splash pad and playground for kids, fitness center, bocce ball, pickle-ball/tennis courts, a clubhouse of social activities, food truck nights and much more.  Conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, and downtown Ft. Myers makes this a perfect home for all.
